und:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#F3F781;\"|\n| \n|-\n! Metisha\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#BDBDBD;\"|\n| style=\"background:#F3F781;\"|\n| \n|-\n|}\n\n==== Notes ====\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#A9D8F5|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" is featured in this episode.</small>\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#F3F781|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" arrives on the beach.</small>\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#9FF781|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" has an ex arrive on the beach.</small>\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#D396FE|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" has two exes arrive on the beach.</small>\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#FAAC58|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" arrives on the beach and has an ex arrive during the same episode.</small>\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#FA8072|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" leaves the beach.</small>\n:  <small>Key: {{Color box|#8181F7|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" has an ex arrive on the beach and leaves during the same episode.</small>\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#F888FD|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" arrives on the beach and leaves during the same episode.</small>\n: <small>Key: {{Color box|#BDBDBD|border=darkgray}} = \"Cast member\" does not feature in this episode.</small>\n\n==Episodes==\n{{see also|List of Ex on the Beach episodes}}\n<onlyinclude>{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|- style=\"color:black\"\n! style=\"background